OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome late
OL,6,Fevening brightness as clear periods
OL,7,Fdevelop and winds begin to slowly
OL,8,Fease. Any residual showers will
OL,9,Fgradually fade to leave a dry and
OL,10,Fchilly night.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FMostly dry but rather
OL,13,Fcloudy, although some afternoon
OL,14,Fbrighter intervals. Winds
OL,15,Fstrengthening, with hill and coastal
OL,16,Fgales developing into the evening as a
OL,17,Fnarrow, heavy rain band moves east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
