OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FStrong
OL,6,Fwinds and coastal gales easing Sunday
OL,7,Fmorning, followed by scattered
OL,8,Fblustery showers, briefly wintry over
OL,9,Fhigher ground. Sunshine and lighter
OL,10,Fwinds Monday; breezier Tuesday but dry
OL,11,Fand sunny. Warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
